  "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "When transactions fail to make it in to a block, **owned** txs (i.e. txs that were submitted by the user - but not necessarily own the key) need to be resend every now and again. \n\nAdditionally during the process of nonce checking and removal of low nonce txs, we also need to check in the **owned** pool and remove them, making sure no bad txs get resubmitted.\n",
